            Steadfast in our mission
          </h3>
          
          <div class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg text-charcoal-light leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              To help real estate and mortgage professionals stop wasting money on disconnected AI tools and start 
